## 🔮 Preview

```python
# Coming soon to py-agent-server
from py_agent_server import MCPServer

server = MCPServer()

@server.tool("calculator")
def calculate(operation: str, a: float, b: float):
    return {"result": a + b if operation == "add" else a * b}

server.run(port=8080)
```

